    "SUMMARY": "Ivan Yevhenovych Petriak (Ukrainian: Іван Євгенович Петряк; born 13 March 1994) is a Ukrainian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Polissya Zhytomyr on loan from Shakhtar Donetsk. Since 2012, he has played for the junior and youth national team of Ukraine. In March 2016, he made his senior debut for the Ukraine national team."
